        "Id": "749be814-58b9-46a4-a78e-c8657d410673",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Raider of the Labyrinthine Ark",
        "Location": "LOCATION_NORTHSEA",
        "PublicId": "121656208692",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/theark/scene_magpie.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository d0ca45fa-9795-41c0-9abf-bbbbb8b714e8).Image",
        "Description": "This contract is not for the feint of heart 47. You&apos;ll be sneaking all throughout the castle swarming with guests and guards, on an island you were never even meant to reach. Even worse, complications with our laundry department require you never leave your suit. Once they realize people are dying, they will lock up every exit, and you will need to flag down a helicopter to leave. Good luck.\r\rNote: To get the helicopter exit, you need a flare found in the small square room on the left of floor 4",
